● 🎮 AI Game Engine - Project Overview

  🚀 What It Does

  Complete AI-powered 2D game generation platform that creates playable games from natural language descriptions using DeepSeek AI, with a
  professional game engine, visual wizard interface, and export capabilities.

  ✨ Key Features

  - 4-Step Wizard: Visual style → Complexity → Theme → Generation
  - Universal Game Engine: Physics, collisions, particles, audio
  - Smart AI Integration: Handles 4K limits with continuation
  - Theme System: 6 visual styles × 6 themes × 4 complexity levels
  - Professional Export: Standalone HTML5 games
  - Robust Fallbacks: Always delivers working games

  📁 Project Structure

  🎮 AI Game Engine/
  ├── 📦 public/
  │   └── vite.svg                    # App icon
  ├── 📂 src/
  │   ├── 📄 main.tsx                 # React app entry point
  │   ├── 📄 index.css                # Global styles + animations
  │   ├── 📄 App.tsx                  # Main app with 4 tabs (Wizard/Prompt/Editor/Preview)
  │   ├── 🎯 components/
  │   │   ├── GameWizard.tsx          # 4-step game generation wizard
  │   │   ├── AIPrompt.tsx            # Basic prompt interface
  │   │   ├── GameEditor.tsx          # Visual game editor
  │   │   ├── Preview.tsx             # Playable game preview
  │   │   ├── ParticleBackground.tsx  # Animated background
  │   │   └── GameDebugger.tsx        # Debug panel for troubleshooting
  │   ├── 🎮 engine/
  │   │   ├── GameEngine.ts           # Universal 2D game engine
  │   │   └── ParticleSystem.ts       # Particle effects system
  │   └── 🤖 services/
  │       ├── deepseek.ts             # Basic DeepSeek API integration
  │       └── enhancedGameGeneration.ts # Advanced AI generation with themes
  ├── 📝 Config Files
  │   ├── package.json                # Dependencies & scripts
  │   ├── vite.config.ts             # Vite bundler config
  │   ├── tailwind.config.js         # CSS framework config
  │   └── tsconfig.json              # TypeScript config

  🎯 Core Components

  🧙 GameWizard - Professional 4-step interface
  🎮 GameEngine - Universal engine runs any generated game🤖 Enhanced Generation - Smart AI with theme libraries
  ✨ Particle System - Visual effects for all actions
  🐛 Debug System - Real-time game data inspection

  🚀 User Flow

  1. Wizard → Choose style/complexity/theme
  2. AI Generate → Creates complete game JSON
  3. Engine Render → Physics + particles + audio
  4. Play → Full interactive experience
  5. Export → Standalone HTML5 game

  Result: From idea to playable game in 60 seconds! 🎮✨